      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend the Congressional Budget Act of 1974 to establish a point of order to prohibit the extension of the public debt limit unless a concurrent resolution on the budget has been agreed to and is in effect.</title>
